from reportlab.platypus import SimpleDocTemplate, Paragraph, Spacer
from reportlab.lib.styles import getSampleStyleSheet

file = "deep_breathing_meditation_story.pdf"

styles = getSampleStyleSheet()

title = "Creative Expression – The Power of Deep Breathing and Dhyan"

story_text = """
Arjun was a college student who always felt stressed because of exams,
assignments, and expectations. His mind was always filled with worries
about the future and fear of failure.

One evening after receiving poor marks in a test, Arjun sat alone in the
college garden feeling frustrated. His heart was racing and his mind
was full of negative thoughts.

While sitting there, he noticed an elderly man peacefully sitting under
a tree with his eyes closed. Curious, Arjun asked him how he remained so
calm in life.

The man smiled and said, "The mind becomes restless when we forget to
pause. Try deep breathing."

He asked Arjun to sit comfortably, close his eyes, and take a slow deep
breath. Arjun inhaled slowly and then released the breath gently.

After repeating this for a few minutes, Arjun noticed something amazing.
His mind became calmer and his heartbeat slowed down.

The man then explained meditation, or Dhyan. Meditation helps us observe
our thoughts without reacting to them.

From that day, Arjun started practicing deep breathing and meditation
for a few minutes every day. Slowly he became more focused, calm, and
emotionally balanced.

Whenever he faced challenges, he paused, took deep breaths, and allowed
his mind to relax before making decisions.

Arjun realized that problems may not disappear, but with deep breathing
and meditation, the mind becomes strong enough to face them peacefully.
"""

content = []

content.append(Paragraph(title, styles['Title']))
content.append(Spacer(1, 20))

for line in story_text.split("\n"):
    content.append(Paragraph(line, styles['BodyText']))
    content.append(Spacer(1, 10))

pdf = SimpleDocTemplate(file)
pdf.build(content)

print("PDF Created Successfully!")
